                         Object value)
        Set the value to ConfigurationSection. This will also affect the values in newContext()

        WARNING: If root (Configuration) unsupported this value. Then will throw a Exception in Configuration.store(OutputStream) Configuration.store(java.io.Writer) Configuration.store(File) Configuration.store(Path)

        参数:

        value - The value.
        返回:
